      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:3:31:12",
      "text": [
        " كَانَ عَلِيٌّ ( عليه السلام ) يَجْلِدُ الْحُرَّ وَ الْعَبْدَ وَ الْيَهُودِيَّ وَ النَّصْرَانِيَّ فِي الْخَمْرِ ثَمَانِينَ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Abu Al Magra, from Abu Baseer, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘Ali<sup>asws</sup> used to whipe the free, and the slave, and the Jew, and the Christian, regarding the wine, eighty (lashes)’."
        ]
      }
